    <item>
      <title>特朗普回归前，加拿大人对经济越来越悲观</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/canadians-are-growing-pessimistic-about-economy-ahead-of-trump-s-return</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普的关税威胁给美国最大的贸易伙伴之一带来了不确定性，加拿大人对经济走向的乐观程度比一年多前有所下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/canadians-are-growing-pessimistic-about-economy-ahead-of-trump-s-return</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡洛斯·斯利姆在 2024 年投资 10 亿美元，增强石油投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/carlos-slim-invested-1-billion-in-2024-to-supercharge-oil-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉丁美洲首富卡洛斯·斯利姆今年投入 10 亿美元扩大其原油生产和炼制业务，因为他认为对化石燃料的需求不会很快消失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/carlos-slim-invested-1-billion-in-2024-to-supercharge-oil-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长斯图纳拉斯表示降息步伐应循序渐进</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/ecb-s-stournaras-says-pace-of-rate-cuts-should-be-gradual</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员亚尼斯·斯图纳拉斯表示，欧洲央行降低借贷成本的举措应该是“渐进的”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/ecb-s-stournaras-says-pace-of-rate-cuts-should-be-gradual</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 12:28:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者重新审视战略，萨索尔或将遭遇最严重年度跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/-sol-sj-south-africa-s-sasol-set-for-worst-annual-drop-on-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者正在权衡南非最大的燃料和化学品制造商萨索尔 (Sasol Ltd.) 降低环境和运营风险的计划，该公司股价有望创下有史以来最差的年度表现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/-sol-sj-south-africa-s-sasol-set-for-worst-annual-drop-on-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 12:23:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>可可市场恢复上涨，但产量担忧仍未消退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/cocoa-market-resumes-gains-as-production-concerns-linger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于供应担忧继续导致昂贵市场的剧烈波动，可可期货在创下 10 月份以来最大单周跌幅后恢复上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/cocoa-market-resumes-gains-as-production-concerns-linger</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 12:17:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
