      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 12:11:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>年终假期前欧洲股市交投清淡下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/european-stocks-drop-as-traders-watch-inflation-ecb-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2024 年倒数第二个交易日，欧洲股市小幅走低，这一年该地区股市小幅上涨，与华尔街的看涨反弹形成鲜明对比。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/european-stocks-drop-as-traders-watch-inflation-ecb-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 08:22:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙通胀加速，支持欧洲央行逐步降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/spanish-inflation-accelerates-backing-gradual-ecb-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙 12 月份通胀率升幅超出预期，受基数效应影响，通胀率连续第二个月维持在 2% 以上，这为逐步降息提供了依据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/spanish-inflation-accelerates-backing-gradual-ecb-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
